        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Test conditions Gradation 2 — experimental conditions documented and traceable",
        "description": "Experimental flow rates, fluid properties, and rotational speeds are documented with measurement uncertainty. Traceability to NIST-calibrated instruments is confirmed."
