      },
      "rationale": "The RH index is computed from the power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) applied to Lagrangian particle trajectories. This QoI directly supports the clinical decision criterion (RH < 1 vs. predicate device) and is the accepted metric in FDA guidance on CFD for blood-contacting devices."
