      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "scoped-out",
      "rationale": "Use error is scoped out at MRL 2 because the simulation was executed by a single experienced analyst following a documented simulation protocol (SOP-CFD-GCBP-v3). Independent peer review of simulation setup parameters was conducted. No user-configurable parameters were identified as having material influence on the RH QoI beyond those already addressed in the model inputs factor."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/factor/mf-cou1",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
