      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty (turbulence model selection, hemolysis constitutive model) is scoped out at MRL 2 for this COU. A sensitivity study comparing SST k-omega and realizable k-epsilon turbulence models showed less than 4% difference in peak RH across all operating points, indicating low model-form sensitivity. Full model-form assessment is deferred to a planned MRL 3 submission."
